tvdinner (0.1.0-19) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Fix Windows portability gaps: bundle the DejaVu fonts as package
    data instead of reading /usr/share/fonts/truetype/dejavu (drops
    the fonts-dejavu-core dependency, now redundant), use %APPDATA%
    for the EPG shift config path on Windows, and only apply the
    X11/Wayland gpu_context override on Linux -- it's a hard mpv
    option error, not a graceful no-op, on Windows builds of libmpv.
    Confirmed working end-to-end via a plain pip install on Windows.
  * Add a GitHub Actions workflow to build and publish .deb/.rpm
    release packages automatically on version tag pushes

